<paragraph blockId="33.[151,1436,898,1480]" pageId="33" pageNumber="34">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,224,898,923]" inLineHeading="true" pageId="33" pageNumber="34" reason="1">Color.</emphasis>
Yellowish white. Two small round spots on vertex and posterior part of pronotum, black. Two spots on corium, one spot at tip of clavus and spots on some veins pale fuscous. Pronotum with minute punctures.
</paragraph>
